    "plainEnglish": "This code describes cancer that has developed in the long bones of the leg (such as the thighbone or shinbone), but the specific leg (left or right) has not been identified in the medical record. These cancers typically arise from bone cells themselves and can cause pain, swelling, and sometimes fractures in the affected leg.",
