    "whoUses": "Oncologists, orthopedic surgeons, and pathologists use this code when diagnosing and treating bone cancer patients. This code commonly appears on medical records and EOB statements for patients undergoing chemotherapy, radiation, surgery, or follow-up care for malignant bone tumors.",
