    "whoUses": "Dermatologists, surgical oncologists, and primary care physicians commonly diagnose and treat SCC and use this code. It frequently appears on patient EOB statements for biopsies, excisions, or other skin cancer treatments, and is one of the most common skin cancer codes in medical billing.",
