    "whoUses": "Oncologists, dermatologists, and infectious disease specialists commonly use this code when diagnosing and treating Kaposi's sarcoma, particularly in patients with HIV/AIDS. This code frequently appears on EOB statements for patients receiving chemotherapy, immunotherapy, or other cancer treatments for this condition.",
