    "whoUses": "Oncologists, surgical oncologists, and general surgeons use this code when diagnosing and treating abdominal nerve cancer, typically after imaging studies and biopsies confirm malignancy. This code commonly appears on patient EOB statements as it represents a significant cancer diagnosis requiring chemotherapy, radiation, and/or surgical intervention.",
