    "whoUses": "Urologists, oncologists, and surgical oncologists use this code when diagnosing and treating testicular cord cancers. It commonly appears on EOB statements for patients undergoing inguinal orchiectomy (surgical removal of the testicle and cord) and oncology consultations or treatments.",
