    "whoUses": "Oncologists, ophthalmologists, and ophthalmologic oncologists use this code during diagnosis, treatment planning, and follow-up care for eye cancer patients. This code is commonly seen on EOB statements for patients undergoing chemotherapy, radiation, or surgical treatment for malignant eye tumors, as well as for specialist consultations and imaging studies.",
