    "whoUses": "Oncologists, neuro-oncologists, neurosurgeons, and endocrinologists use this code when diagnosing and treating pituitary cancer. It commonly appears on EOB statements for patients undergoing imaging studies, biopsies, surgical procedures, chemotherapy, or radiation therapy related to pituitary malignancies.",
