    "whoUses": "Oncologists, neurologists, and neurosurgeons use this code when cancer has metastasized to the brain's protective lining. It commonly appears in the medical records and insurance EOBs of cancer patients undergoing brain imaging or treatment, indicating the cancer has progressed beyond its original site.",
