    "whoUses": "Oncologists, gynecologic oncologists, and gynecologists use this code when treating patients whose cancer has spread to the right ovary. It commonly appears on EOB statements for patients undergoing chemotherapy, radiation, or surgery for metastatic cancer, and is often used alongside the code for the primary (original) cancer site.",
