    "whoUses": "Oncologists, internists, and endocrinologists use this code when documenting metastatic cancer involving the adrenal glands during treatment planning and follow-up care. This code frequently appears on EOB statements for patients with advanced cancer who have undergone imaging (CT/MRI) confirming adrenal involvement, as it affects staging, prognosis, and treatment decisions.",
